Constructor Detail

ClientXMLOperationError

public ClientXMLOperationError(org.w3c.dom.Node errorNode)
Constructs the object from its XML representation. The (optional) child elements are:
  • node: the XML node that caused the failure
  • error: the exception. This has the follwoing substructure:
    • msg
    • type
    • code (optional)
    • trace

errorNode -
